videos.headline: UCLA's Holmes ejected for targeting
videos.description: Darnay Holmes leads with his helmet high on a hit on Phillip Lindsay and is ejected for targeting after review.

videos.headline: Montez connects with Lindsay for Colorado TD
videos.description: Steven Montez gets Colorado on the board with a 21-yard touchdown to Phillip Lindsay.

videos.headline: Lasley loses a defender for 44 yards
videos.description: Jordan Lasley shakes off a tackler on a 44-yard pass from Josh Rosen for UCLA.

videos.headline: Rosen finds Roberts to tie it for UCLA
videos.description: Josh Rosen throws a 12-yard touchdown in the corner to Austin Roberts to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: Montez throws to Shenault Jr. for 42 yards
videos.description: Steven Montez finds Laviksa Shenault Jr. up the sideline for 42 yards for Colorado.

videos.headline: Lasley down at the 1 on big flea-flicker
videos.description: Jordan Lasley gets tackled at the one-yard line on a 46-yard flea-flicker from Josh Rosen.

videos.headline: Starks jumps the pile for a TD
videos.description: Jalen Starks jumps over the line for a one-yard UCLA touchdown.

videos.headline: MacIntyre: 'Montez made some good plays'
videos.description: Colorado coach Mike MacIntyre saw his quarterback Steven Montez make some good plays in the first half against UCLA.

videos.headline: Jamabo rushes for UCLA TD
videos.description: Soso Jamabo takes it in from two yards out for a UCLA touchdown increasing UCLA's lead to 21-10.

videos.headline: Colorado's Laguda leaves game on late hit
videos.description: Afolabi Laguda has to leave the game after a late hit from Jordan Lasley.

videos.headline: Lindsay smashes through for a Colorado TD
videos.description: Phillip Lindsay breaks through the line for a two-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Montez gets a big gain into the red zone
videos.description: Steven Montez takes it 37 yards inside UCLA's red zone before going out of bounds.
